modDescription:
Quadra V-Tech from Cyberpunk 2077 in 7 Days to Die. This is a single vehicle mod. The car is set up to be fast, powerful and a lot of traction.

It is often a lot of fun but its not an off road [vehicle](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-vehicles/). Whether this is one of your favorite things from Cyberpunk 2077 or you just like fast cars, this is a nice [car](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-car-mods/) for 7 Days to Die. At the moment there are no crafting recipes for this car but it is planned.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/adredengaming/adreden_modlets/-/archive/master/adreden_modlets-master.zip?path=Adredens_QuadraVTech)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/16328-adredens-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Adreden Gaming](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/adreden-gaming/)
